jinda02.res_review2: A recently opened coffee shop near Lat Krabang 54 (near the Family Mart and foot bridge).  This is one of few if only coffee shops in the area where you can sit indoors.  Coffee prices are affordabe at around 55 baht for a large cup of coffee.  The shop opens arround  6 a.m. which is earlier than most.
